>同时杯盖上面设计两个金属触点可以使用磁吸<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/chongdianqi/" target="_blank">充电器</a>充电，充电</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Baskerville;">2</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">.</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Baskerville;">5</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">小时，可以使用大约两周时间。</span></span></p><p itemprop="description"><span style="font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 14px;"></span></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/aekw25gk/pic_6/' target='_blank'><img alt="【Simita施密特智能保温水杯】喝水！一定要提醒你！" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd8e2b926fe45300.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description" style="margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;text-indent:27px;font-size:12px;line-height:normal;font-family:&#39;PingFang SC&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">不过不要看是充电产品，智能保温杯全身支持</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Baskerville;">ipx7</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">级防水，全身都可以进行水洗的。</span></span></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/aekw25gk/pic_7/' target='_blank'><img alt="【Simita施密特智能保温水杯】喝水！一定要提醒你！" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd8e2dab2c3d8140.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description" style="margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;text-indent:27px;font-size:12px;line-height:normal;font-family:&#39;PingFang SC&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">而介绍了设计外形，作为水杯基本要求的就是内部材质和保温效果了，灵晞智能保温杯内壁采用</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Baskerville;">316</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">不锈钢材质，特别提示在耐热程度上</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Baskerville;">316</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">耐高温要比</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Baskerville;">304</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">多了一倍以上。</span></span></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/aekw25gk/pic_8/' target='_blank'><img alt="【Simita施密特智能保温水杯】喝水！一定要提醒你！" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd8e31adc427565.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description" style="margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;text-indent:27px;font-size:12px;line-height:normal;font-family:&#39;PingFang SC&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">内盖使用橡胶材质也是食品级别，毕竟涉及入口，安全问题可是马虎不得，内盖采用内螺旋设计，密封效果非常不错，一般放在包中完全没有问题，不用担心。而在保温方便，虽然哥特一般是在室内使用，</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Baskerville;">100</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">度开水倒入后，基本全天都有热水喝，保温效果非常不错。</span></span></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/aekw25gk/pic_9/' target='_blank'><img alt="【Simita施密特智能保温水杯】喝水！一定要提醒你！" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd8e359154c12675.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description" style="margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;text-indent:27px;font-size:12px;line-height:normal;font-family:&#39;PingFang SC&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">同时在不开启</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Baskerville;">app</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">的情况下，轻触杯盖，根据环圈的指示灯就可以知道大概水温了，红灯表示水温在</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Baskerville;">66</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">度以上，橙色灯表示在</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Baskerville;">37</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">度到</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Baskerville;">65</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">度之间，绿灯表示在</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Baskerville;">36</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular;">度以下，对于我这个特别喜欢喝热水的人，特别好用。<span class="rangySelectionBoundary" style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 0;">﻿</span></span></span></p><p itemprop="description"><span style="line-height: 0; font-size: 14px;">﻿</span></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/aekw25gk/pic_10/' target='_blank'><img alt="【Simita施密特智能保温水杯】喝水！一定要提醒你！" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd8e38eb8d3f7534.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; text-indent: 27px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">施密特灵晞智能保温杯号称为全球首款<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/chuandaishebei/" target="_blank">物联网</a>智能保温水杯，它可以利用智能连接帮助我们。虽然保温杯本身没有内置<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/maikefeng/" target="_blank">麦克风</a>，但是通过<a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/45987/" data-brandid="45987" target="_blank">天猫精灵</a><span style="font-size: 14px;">app连接到</span>天猫精灵音响，就开启了全面智能模式，杯子不仅可以通过天猫精灵音箱来询问水杯电量以及水温，还可以在<span style="font-size: 14px;">APP中设定提醒喝水，到时间后会有声音提示，非常贴心。同时在在app中还可以查看个人喝水情况，对于那些不爱喝水的同学们，男朋友的关爱随时在耳边。</span></span></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/aekw25gk/pic_11/' target='_blank'><img alt="【Simita施密特智能保温水杯】喝水！一定要提醒你！" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd8e4038c5084876.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/aekw25gk/pic_12/' target='_blank'><img alt="【Simita施密特智能保温水杯】喝水！一定要提醒你！" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd8e402dcca62870.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-le