38.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><dir class="insert-outer " res-data-id="2807860"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="【秋冬必备】男士面霜哪个牌子最好用？" class="res_smzdm" src="//res.smzdm.com/images/card/default.png"/></span><span class="embed-card-info  res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">资生堂男士uno面霜<strong class="price res_smzdm">69.9元</strong></span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">天猫国际</span><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去购买</span></span></span></span></dir><p itemprop="description"> <br/></p><h3>  5. <a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/2197/" data-brandid="2197" target="_blank">科颜氏</a>高保湿面霜（清爽版）</h3><p itemprop="description">油皮一定要入这款面霜，质地是半透明的啫喱状，因为是无油配方，上脸会很清爽，很好推开，吸收也很快，毫无油腻感也不会粘腻，保湿度会弱一些，但对于本身皮肤比较油的男生来说也不是坏事，用起来是无负担的，就是价格有点贵</p><p itemprop="description">（如果冬天是比较干的，那我推荐买高保湿那款，我个人用了，也觉得很滋润，但不会太粘绸）</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a6lxvr2o/pic_6/' target='_blank'><img alt="【秋冬必备】男士面霜哪个牌子最好用？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/12/5fd43efde798a2934.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><dir class="insert-outer " res-data-id="2802094"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="【秋冬必备】男士面霜哪个牌子最好用？" class="res_smzdm" src="//qna.smzdm.com/202012/12/5fd4404f6b2696955.jpg_e680.jpg"/></span><span class="embed-card-info  res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">【立即抢购】科颜氏高保湿清爽面霜保湿补水控油不油腻<strong class="price res_smzdm">315元</strong></span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">天猫精选</span><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去购买</span></span></span></span></dir><h3>6. <a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/973/" data-brandid="973" target="_blank">御泥坊</a>男士面霜</h3><p itemprop="description">一抹就能匀开，不会很黏腻，有点像乳液的质地，比较水润，味道很好闻，是淡淡的香味，保湿效果很不错，上脸可以保持一整天脸不会紧绷</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a6lxvr2o/pic_7/' target='_blank'><img alt="【秋冬必备】男士面霜哪个牌子最好用？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/12/5fd43efdd4dfc1118.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><dir class="insert-outer " res-data-id="2802098"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="【秋冬必备】男士面霜哪个牌子最好用？" class="res_smzdm" src="//res.smzdm.com/images/card/default.png"/></span><span class="embed-card-info  res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">御泥坊男士面霜<strong class="price res_smzdm">79元</strong></span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">天猫精选</span><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去购买</span></span></span></span></dir><p itemprop="description"> <br/></p><p itemprop="description">     无论男女，一个好的皮肤状态能让人看上去干净清爽，也让人看着阳光。如果满脸痘痘还泛着油光，又或者脸上起皮，真的会让人望而却步，所以这个冬天好好保护自己的皮肤吧！毕竟现在大家都开始很注重自己的形象啦~</p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><br/>
