单相机单机身黑色镀铬20002<strong class="price res_smzdm">64900元</strong></span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">京东</span><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去购买</span></span></span></span></dir><dir class="insert-outer " res-data-id="2807997"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="穷人的快乐你不懂，2020我只为徕卡M-P 240痴迷癫狂" class="res_smzdm" src="//qna.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd97eae04f308911.jpg_e680.jpg"/></span><span class="embed-card-info  res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">徕卡（Leica）相机M10-P专业旁轴经典全画幅数码照相机20021<strong class="price res_smzdm">61000元</strong></span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">京东</span><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去购买</span></span></span></span></dir><dir class="insert-outer " res-data-id="2807998"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="穷人的快乐你不懂，2020我只为徕卡M-P 240痴迷癫狂" class="res_smzdm" src="//qna.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd97ebfb71a79711.jpg_e680.jpg"/></span><span class="embed-card-info  res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">徕卡（Leica）M10全画幅旁轴数码相机/微单相机单机身黑色（纯粹摄影）<strong class="price res_smzdm">55000元</strong></span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">京东</span><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去购买</span></span></span></span></dir><dir class="insert-outer " res-data-id="2808004"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="穷人的快乐你不懂，2020我只为徕卡M-P 240痴迷癫狂" class="res_smzdm" src="//a.zdmimg.com/202008/27/5f47cf89f13eb6.jpg_e680.jpg"/></span><span class="embed-card-info res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">买徕卡相机又差点被骗，实战经验教你高效避坑！</span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm">创作立场声明：真实经验分享1、起因很简单▲2020年了，徕卡M机型都更新到M10-R了，即便也有众多粉丝为M10、M10-P叫好，我还是迷恋M240系列。要说整体色彩科学，怎么不玩M9系列？脱膜啊，就算返厂更换了依然会，而且徕卡基本上不会再管了。显得老掉牙的M9系列，就算色彩再好，我个人选择果断退烧</span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">亨力亨力</span><span class="card-inline-split">|</span><span class="group-data res_smzdm"> <em>赞</em>55</span><span class="group-data res_smzdm"> <em>评论</em>74</span><span class="group-data res_smzdm"> <em>收藏</em>119</span><span class="card-btn-light res_smzdm">查看详情</span></span></span></span></dir><p itemprop="description">▲</p><p itemprop="description">- 如果你真想体验徕卡的摄影精髓，尽量首选M机型，SL和Q系列<a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/247/" data-brandid="247" target="_blank">松下</a>味儿太浓，别问为什么，别问徕卡和松下的关系……<br/></p><p itemprop="description">- M240系列现在已经停产了，如果要买M-P，尽量选51编码开头的，避坑攻略我也写过看上面的链接。</p><p itemprop="description">- 2019年发布的M-E 240就非常棒，去掉了框线拨杆品控问题更少，取景器放大倍率也增大了，我个人认为它是目前整个M240系列中最值得买的机型。</p><p itemprop="description">- M-P 240的品控问题真挺多，一定记得检查黄斑对焦是否失效、峰值线是否精准、传感器是否坏点坏线。</p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description">以上。</p><blockquote><p itemprop="description">小编注：本文作者 @亨力亨力 是什么值得买首席生活家，他的个人自媒体信息为：</p><p itemprop="description">新浪微博：@hi亨力</p><p itemprop="description">扶持推广个人品牌是生活家新增福利，更多详细内容请了解<a href="https://zhiyou.smzdm.com/author/">生活家页面</a>。欢迎大家踊跃申请生活家，生活家中表现优异的用户还将有机会成为『首席生活家』，欢迎有着特别生活经验的值友们踊跃加入生活家大家庭！</p></blockquote><p itemprop="description"><br/></p>
