➜冠希的Juice店，街牌年末打折挺狠的，别维信了，这里转也可以...
https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7o0d09/	26321
<p itemprop="description">*封面摘自HYPEBEAST，为Juice成都开业时照片</p><p itemprop="description">在值得买发东西，不发消费类内容发啥呢？</p><p itemprop="description">所以今天挤出发街头新品资讯的空档，再和大家分享个折扣信息。</p><p itemprop="description">昨天已经和各位值友草草分享了加拿大买手店SSENSE的好物好价捡漏，其实当时我发现冠希哥的Juicestore也在打折。</p><h2 id="cl_0"><strong>Juicestore by CLOT</strong></h2><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7o0d09/pic_2/' target='_blank'><img alt="冠希的Juice店，街牌年末打折挺狠的，别维信了，这里转也可以..." src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd96b46be5a47926.png_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">Juice是陈冠希和其忠诚的老弟潘世亨在2003年创立的街头品牌CLOT（凝结）的专卖店同时也是正规街牌代理商，在中国香港、上海、北京、成都都有门店，当然，他们线上店铺也在经营。<br/></p><p itemprop="description">查看一下他们站对内地消费的便利度：</p><p itemprop="description">1、支持汉字和人民币显示<br/>2、支持支付宝和微信支付<br/>3、支持直邮，但建议转运</p><p itemprop="description">大概扫清了部分值友选购的顾虑，好，那我就直切主题。</p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7o0d09/pic_3/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202012/16/5fd972cdb7c7b4368.png_e680.jpg" title="" alt="编辑这篇文章的时候，这款绿拖鞋还在..."/></a>编辑这篇文章的时候，这款绿拖鞋还在...</span></p><p itemprop="description">品牌依然以先数字，后字母排序的方式呈现，库存少、品牌过于经典和大众的单品不呈现~<br/></p><h2 id="cl_1">Aimé Leon Dore</h2><p itemprop="description">ALD，这个牌子在站内时尚账号花小编和我自己的文章中都有出现，在纽约能够赶超KITH的又有个优雅系高端街头品牌。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7o0d09/pic_4/' target='_blank'><img alt="冠希的Juice店，街牌年末打折挺狠的，别维信了，这里转也可以..." src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd98206849f83012.jpg_e680.jpg" _size="255261"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description">这款染色泡泡纱短袖衬衫是ALD前两年的标志性单品，的确他们的定价是很高的，打了6折还要约1220元，当前L和XL码可选。</p><dir class="insert-outer" res-data-id="2808022"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="冠希的Juice店，街牌年末打折挺狠的，别维信了，这里转也可以..." class="res_smzdm" src="//qna.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd98156510b65202.jpg_e680.jpg"/></span><span class="embed-card-info res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">Aimé Leon Dore-Spray Dye Leisure Shirt</span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">juicestore.com</span><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去看看</span></span></span></span></dir><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7o0d09/pic_5/' target='_blank'><img alt="冠希的Juice店，街牌年末打折挺狠的，别维信了，这里转也可以..." src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd982d003d541264.jpg_e680.jpg" _size="262688"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description">常青藤学院派也是纽约男装品牌必备设计，不过ALD的这款除了字体和配色，更强调了重磅线圈棉的面料选取，20盎司，确实比较厚重了，螺纹有效收紧，正经卫衣一件，当前M码有货，5折价格，约680元，ALD有这个价格不错啦。</p><dir class="insert-outer " res-data-id="2808047"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="冠希的Juice店，街牌年末打折挺狠的，别维信了，这里转也可以..." class="res_smzdm" src="//qna.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd982b92c35b1491.jpg_e680.jpg"/></span><span class="embed-card-info res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">Aime Leon Dore-20oz Terry Collegiate Crewneck</span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">juicestore.com</span><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去看看</span></span></span></span></dir><h2 id="cl_2">ARIES<br/></h2><p itemprop="description">ARIES这个牌子总想推给大家，其实之前INNERSECT也有这个牌子的代理，但是近期好物都下架了，而且SSENSE也所剩无几，但看Juice还有一些经典款可选。</p><p itemprop="description">ARIES这个牌子，首先是个意大利血统的英国街牌，由街头文化领域着名插画师Fergus Purcell和街头文化界女强人Sofia Pantera创立（俩人都可以单独开篇文章写写），品牌格调是80年代流行、反主流叛逆格调，具体呈现形式有染色、标语等等这些街头品牌屡试不爽的设计。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7o0d09/pic_6/' target='_blank'><img alt="冠希的Juice店，街牌年末打折挺狠的，别维信了，这里转也可以..." src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd98d334eb514981.jpg_e680.jpg" _size="209382"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description"> 这件褪色退得像黑牛的T恤，用黑墨印着品牌标志性意大利建筑logo和... JEANS，落肩款，6折价格，约455元，4码齐全。</p><dir class="insert-outer" res-data-id="2808097"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="冠希的Juice店，街牌年末打折挺狠的，别维信了，这里转也可以..." class="res_smzdm" src="//qna.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd98d5d2d4182682.jpg_e680.jpg"/></span><span class="embed-card-info res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">Aries-Jeans S/ST-Shirt</span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">juicestore.com</span><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去看看</span></span></span></span></dir><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7o0d09/pic_7/' target='_blank'><img alt="冠希的Juice店，街牌年末打折挺狠的，别维信了，这里转也可以..." src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd98e3042e4b4431.jpg_e680.jpg" _size="129368"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description">No Problemo是ARIES主推的一个标语，想起那会儿VLONE的一件FRIENDS都能卖得很好...不过ARIES在用料和剪裁上是没有短板的，M/L/XL码有货，6折价，约760元。<br/></p><dir class="insert-outer" res-data-id="2808104"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="冠希的Juice店，街牌年末打折挺狠的，别维信了，这里转也可以..." class="res_smzdm" src="//qna.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd98e5eb1cf93937.jpg_e680.jpg"/></span><span class="embed-card-info res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">Aries-No Problemo Sweat</span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">juicestore.com</span><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去看看</span></span></span></span></dir><p itemprop="description">还有另一个颜色，还贵一点，约910元。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7o0d09/pic_8/' target='_blank'><img alt="冠希的Juice店，街牌年末打折挺狠的，别维信了，这里转也可以..." src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd98f1ed2c45150.jpg_e680.jpg" _size="208578"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description" style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12px;">没有M码</span></p><dir class="insert-outer" res-data-id="2808111"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="冠希的Juice店，街牌年末打折挺狠的，别维信了，这里转也可以..." class="res_smzdm" src="//qna.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd98faaec54b6550.jpg_e680.jpg"/></span><span class="embed-card-info res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">Aries-No Problemo Tie Dye Sweat</span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">juicestore.com</span><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去看看</span></span></span></span></dir><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7o0d09/pic_9/' target='_blank'><img alt="冠希的Juice店，街牌年末打折挺狠的，别维信了，这里转也可以..." src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd98f6d9193d1054.jpg_e680.jpg" _size="124882"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description">借用THRASHER滑板杂志字体的设计不要太多，ARIES这次也偷懒一次，不过🦂印花挺有意思且插画形式比较复古，这是一件长袖T恤，6折约410元，M码起有货。 </p><dir class="insert-outer" res-data-id="2808110"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="冠希的Juice店，街牌年末打折挺狠的，别维信了，这里转也可以..." class="res_smzdm" src="//qna.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd98f854c7579655.jpg_e680.jpg"/></span><span class="embed-card-info res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">Aries-ScorpionL/ST-Shirt</span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">juicestore.com</span><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去看看</span></span></span></span></dir><p itemprop="description"> <br/></p><h2 id="cl_3">AWAKE NY</h2><p itemprop="description">AWAKE NY我们在SSENSE的那篇文章介绍过，是Supreme嫡系品牌中的重点品牌之一，和SSENSE中单品不大相同，Juice这里有几件AWAKE和Kappa的“土潮”设计联名，还有一些原价单品，我个人认为也值得推荐给大家。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7o0d09/pic_10/' target='_blank'><img alt="冠希的Juice店，街牌年末打折挺狠的，别维信了，这里转也可以..." src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd991b1ba2f74421.png_e680.jpg" _size="1048678"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description">这顶针织帽名叫CHINATOWN SCRIPT，也就代表纽约的唐人街啦，还有其他颜色可选，还有纽约尼克斯配色，但对于值友来说，低调点的颜色还能接受，售价约340元。 </p><dir class="insert-outer" res-data-id="2808119"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="冠希的Juice店，街牌年末打折挺狠的，别维信了，这里转也可以..." class="res_smzdm" src="//qna.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd99220a18c1932.jpg_e680.jpg"/></span><span class="embed-card-info res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">Awake NY-Chinatown Script Beanie</span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">juicestore.com</span><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去看看</span></span></span></span></dir><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7o0d09/pic_11/' target='_blank'><img alt="冠希的Juice店，街牌年末打折挺狠的，别维信了，这里转也可以..." src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd99259d8aa06471.png_e680.jpg" _size="672479"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description">和AWAKE给人第一眼美观的品牌或许只有Verdy的Girls dont Cry或者Have a good time了，这顶五片帽，简简单单，蓝底白字体logo很讨喜，约340元。 </p><dir class="insert-outer" res-data-id="2808126"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="冠希的Juice店，街牌年末打折挺狠的，别维信了，这里转也可以..." class="res_smzdm" src="//qna.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd9930aa09ed167.jpg_e680.jpg"/></span><span class="embed-card-info res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">Awake NY-Classic Logo Camp Cap</span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">juicestore.com</span><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去看看</span></span></span></span></dir><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7o0d09/pic_12/' target='_blank'><img alt="冠希的Juice店，街牌年末打折挺狠的，别维信了，这里转也可以..." src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd99340ed8a38435.jpg_e680.jpg" _size="219018"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7o0d09/pic_13/' target='_blank'><img alt="冠希的Juice店，街牌年末打折挺狠的，别维信了，这里转也可以..." src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd99340e0ae5150.jpg_e680.jpg" _size="278512"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description">与Kappa联名这件涤纶材质的T恤戏太多了，化纤材质也适合运动时穿着，5折价，约340元。<br/></p><dir class="insert-outer" res-data-id="2808132"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="冠希的Juice店，街牌年末打折挺狠的，别维信了，这里转也可以..." class="res_smzdm" src="//qna.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd99363359dd2442.jpg_e680.jpg"/></span><span class="embed-card-info res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">Awake NY x Kappa-Evander Jersey</span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">juicestore.com</span><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去看看</span></span></span></span></dir><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7o0d09/pic_14/' target='_blank'><img alt="冠希的Juice店，街牌年末打折挺狠的，别维信了，这里转也可以..." src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd993da6465c7134.jpg_e680.jpg" _size="232082"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description">这件运动夹克从配色再到拼接设计，无不凸显土气的复古格调，姜文说过：“少要持重，老要狂”，推荐给不在乎配色好不好看更在乎酷不酷的值友们，5折价，550元约。</p><dir class="insert-outer " res-data-id="2808135"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="冠希的Juice店，街牌年末打折挺狠的，别维信了，这里转也可以..." class="res_smzdm" src="//qna.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd993c7b42c54938.jpg_e680.jpg"/></span><span class="embed-card-info res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">Awake NY x Kappa-Eldred Track Jacket</span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">juicestore.com</span><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去看看</span></span></span></span></dir><p itemprop="description"> <br/></p><h2 id="cl_4">BABYLON</h2><p itemprop="description">BABYLON是一个根基比较稳的街头品牌，因为创始人Lee Spielman和Garrett Stevenson是硬核摇滚乐队Trash Talk成员，而且也滑板。但是Juice在售的单品其实是2019年就在INNERSECT上发布过的巴比伦和PSYCHWORLD的联名。而PSYCHWORLD或许就属于无脑潮这类的街牌（Psycho-world，你说呢）。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7o0d09/pic_15/' target='_blank'><img alt="冠希的Juice店，街牌年末打折挺狠的，别维信了，这里转也可以..." src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd9960a33b685734.jpg_e680.jpg" _size="205365"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7o0d09/pic_16/' target='_blank'><img alt="冠希的Juice店，街牌年末打折挺狠的，别维信了，这里转也可以..." src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd9960a1a0c49999.jpg_e680.jpg" _size="177637"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description">这款T恤，除了有恰好呼应INNERSECT展会logo的背部印花，我们可以看到，前面的印花，两品牌logo的字体互换了一下，这种玩法看似耍小聪明，但已经算不错的细节呈现了，码全，6折约350元。 </p><dir class="insert-outer" res-data-id="2808146"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="冠希的Juice店，街牌年末打折挺狠的，别维信了，这里转也可以..." class="res_smzdm" src="//qna.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd9968d862046776.jpg_e680.jpg"/></span><span class="embed-card-info res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">T-Shirt(Type-2)</span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">juicestore.com</span><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去看看</span></span></span></span></dir><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/av7o0d09/pic_17/' target='_blank'><img alt="冠希的Juice店，街牌年末打折挺狠的，别维信了，这里转也可以..." src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd9975fc6ed43978.jpg_e680.jpg" _size="236778"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description">这个设计也有帽衫的版本，S和M码有货，个人认为660块买件帽衫比350块买件T恤值一些，虽然价格都不低啦。</p><dir class="insert-outer" res-data-id="2808148"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="冠希的Juice店，街牌年末打折挺狠的，别维信了，这里转也可以..." class="res_smzdm" src="//qna.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd99787579283998.jpg_e680.jpg"/></span><span class="embed-card-info res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">Psychworld x Babylon-Hoodie(Type-1)</span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls re